<head type="main">Arrival of the Mail from Salt Lake City.</head>

<p>Although our regular files of the <orgName type="newspaper" key="Deseret News">Deseret News</orgName> have not reached us, we have been enabled (thanks to Mr. <persName key="Taft, Daniel">Daniel Taft</persName>, the <placeName type="settlement" key="San Bernardino, CA">San Bernardino</placeName> mail carrier) to procure full files of that paper, up to the 7th October.</p>

<p><seg type="Context" subtype="LDSPersecution"><seg type="Context" subtype="UtahWar">The intelligence is of the utmost importance, as it exhibits the Mormon leaders in almost direct conflict with the United States Government. We intended to place before our readers, this week certain speeches of Presidents <persName key="Young, Brigham">Brigham Young</persName> and <persName key="Kimball, Heber C.">Heber C. Kimball</persName>, but find ourselves, for want of space, compelled to defer them for the present.</seg></seg></p>

</div1>
